 ('2', '2', 'en_us', 'Home', '<p>Kent State Student Media is the brand that represents all the broadcast and film, print, and online content created by Kent State students. Our media partners are  independent, nationally recognized, and nationally award-winning. </p>\n<p>Every student is invited to come join us and gain a professional, practical, and fun experience that will add to their resume. <br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'About Student Media', NULL, '', 'Kent State\'s Independent Student Media Organization', NULL, NULL, '', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/210945217', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Kent State Student Media is the brand that represents all the broadcast and film, print, and online content created by Kent State students. Our media partners are independent, nationally recognized, and nationally award-winning. </p>', 'Advertising With Us', 'Our Media Partners', 'Watch our student-produced video to learn more about Student Media.', NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-05-27 18:34:58', 'f78f163d-6654-40b7-9f92-e347dd1a8a48'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_us', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Kentstatestudentmedia.com. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-01-12 16:12:59', 'dfa73501-ee0c-49a1-9e07-9d9311da2157'),
