 ('10', '10', 'en_us', 'A Magazine', '<p>A Magazine is Kent State\'s publication for all things fashion, beauty and culture on campus and beyond. A focuses on both women\'s and men\'s fashion and has companion website that is updated regularly, providing students with the latest fashion industry and more. It is distributed at Kent State and the Fashion School’s New York studio.<br /></p>', NULL, 'amagksu@gmail.com', '[]', 'Payton', 'Moore', 'Student Leader', NULL, '', 'A Magazine is a visually stunning student-run magazine at Kent State. It is the publication for all things fashion, beauty, accessories and culture on campus and beyond. A focuses on both women\'s and men\'s fashion and has companion website that is updated regularly with extended content and videos, providing students with the latest fashion news. It is distributed at Kent State and the Fashion School’s New York studio.', NULL, NULL, 'mnjkhhghgj', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A Magazine is Kent State’s student-run fashion magazine and is the hub for all things fashion, beauty and culture related.', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-23 21:56:29', '2017-06-01 18:43:57', '6f8e97bf-9f33-417d-ac37-a04cb04c79ba'),
