 ('43', '45', 'en_us', 'Kevin Dilley', '<p>Kevin serves Student Media by providing management of our business and advising operations. He also works with student leaders to set a strategic direction for Student Media and mentors and advises student leaders.  </p>\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:</strong></p>\n<p>If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together.  ~ origin unknown.</p>\n<p><strong>Personal:</strong></p>\n<p>I’ve traveled to Siberia, Malaysia, Mexico and 46 of 50 states in the U.S. I love going places and meeting new people, but I always yearn to return home. For me, that’s in Hudson with my two children, mi media naranja (si, hablo español), and Pancho, my very best friend because, well he’s a dog and I’m a man. I hold degrees in journalism and visual communication from the University of Missouri and Ohio University. I’ve worked as a writer, photojournalist, editor, designer, web designer, project manager, consultant, professor and adviser. I love what I do because I’m constantly inspired by my students who bring ideas, enthusiasm, opportunity and optimism to this place every day.</p>\n<p><strong>I can help you with:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><p>General questions</p></li><li><p>Strategic planning</p></li><li><p>Idea development</p></li><li><p>Budgets</p></li></ul>', NULL, 'kdilley@kent.edu', '[\"director\",\"nonVoting\",\"officeStaff\"]', 'Kevin ', 'Dilley', 'Director of Student Media', NULL, '330-672-4603', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-03-12 16:17:55', '2017-05-04 21:03:34', 'a1f46deb-5b8e-45c2-a2c2-8a7e02d6cc7d'),
