 ('110', '161', 'en_us', 'Student Media Board Members', '<p>The Student Media Board is made up of various stakeholders to ensure that Kent State Student Media is the best that it can be. Voting members include faculty members appointed by the faculty senate, faculty members appointed by the school of journalism and mass communication faculty advisory committee, the JMC director, the CSI director, USG appointees, a graduate senate appointee, JMC undergraduate students, a JMC graduate student and a media professional. All student leaders, student media advisors and the director of student media serve as non-voting members. <br /></p><p>Check out the guidelines, members and meeting minutes below.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Team That Makes It Happen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-22 21:50:41', '2017-05-10 21:41:05', '4ab20dbb-c122-4519-826a-77a8f89c25d6'),
