 ('114', '165', 'en_us', 'Lorie Bednar', '<p>Lorie Bednar joined Kent State’s School of Journalism and Mass Communication in 2015 as an administrative clerk in the Kent State Student Media office. She now shares her time between both offices. (Other information you want to add)</p>\n<p><b>Words to Live By:</b></p>\n<p>Be Where Your Feet Are – Anonymous</p>\n<p><b>Personal</b>:</p>\n<p>Lorie is a graduate of Kent State University and loves everything about her Alma mater. If you don’t find her on campus, chances are you may run into her downtown and throughout Kent, where she lives and enjoys spending time with her husband and three kids. Two of her greatest achievements are winning an Associated Press award for enterprise writing and being the illustrator of a book jacket.</p>\n<p><b>I can help you with:</b></p>\n<ul><li><p>KEYS!</p></li><li><p>Staff lists</p></li><li><p>Job offers</p></li><li><p>Travel</p></li><li>General questions</li></ul>', NULL, '', '[\"officeStaff\"]', 'Lorie', 'Bednar', 'Administrative Clerk', NULL, '330-672-3290', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '5e0b009f-baba-4aef-b7db-adf004400e1c'),
