 ('217', '45', '8', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Kevin Dilley\",\"slug\":\"kevin-dilley\",\"postDate\":1489335420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":[\"23\"],\"1\":\"<p>Kevin serves Student Media by providing management of our business and advising operations. He also works with student leaders to set a strategic direction for Student Media and mentors and advises student leaders. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>Words to Live By:<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together. &nbsp;~ origin unknown.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>Personal:<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I\\u2019ve traveled to Siberia, Malaysia, Mexico and 46 of 50 states in the U.S. I love going places and meeting new people, but I always yearn to return home. For me, that\\u2019s in Hudson with my two children, mi media naranja (si, hablo espa\\u00f1ol), and Pancho, my very best friend because, well he\\u2019s a dog and I\\u2019m a man. I hold degrees in journalism and visual communication from the University of Missouri and Ohio University. I\\u2019ve worked as a writer, photojournalist, editor, designer, web designer, project manager, consultant, professor and adviser. I love what I do because I\\u2019m constantly inspired by my students who bring ideas, enthusiasm, opportunity and optimism to this place every day.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>I can help you with:<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>General questions<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Strategic planning<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Idea development<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Budgets<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"kdilley@kent.edu\",\"5\":[\"director\"],\"6\":\"Kevin \",\"19\":\"\",\"8\":\"Director of Student Media\",\"7\":\"Dilley\",\"10\":\"330-672-4603\"}}', '2017-04-24 17:36:00', '2017-04-24 17:36:00', 'b7db872b-24c1-4d43-9ff4-5f75c0dc8dd5'),
 ('218', '165', '8', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Lorie Bednar\",\"slug\":\"lorie-bednar\",\"postDate\":1493055421,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Lorie Bednar joined Kent State\\u2019s School of Journalism and Mass Communication in 2015 as an administrative clerk in the Kent State Student Media office. She now shares her time between both offices. (Other information you want to add)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>Words to Live By:<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Be Where Your Feet Are \\u2013 Anonymous<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>Personal<\\/b>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Lorie is a graduate of Kent State University and loves everything about her Alma mater. If you don\\u2019t find her on campus, chances are you may run into her downtown and throughout Kent, where she lives and enjoys spending time with her husband and three kids. Two of her greatest achievements are winning an Associated Press award for enterprise writing and being the illustrator of a book jacket.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><b>I can help you with:<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>KEYS!<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Staff lists<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Job offers<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Travel<\\/p><\\/li><li>General questions<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"\",\"5\":[\"officeStaff\"],\"6\":\"Lorie\",\"19\":\"\",\"8\":\"Administrative Clerk\",\"7\":\"Bednar\",\"10\":\"330-672-3290\"}}', '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '8624a234-0a74-4b89-9b54-b1ac2cee63c2'),
