 ('335', '58', '9', '1', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"About Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1492560894,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media empowers students to be the best they can be. Students of any major and grade level are able to join us and gain a fun, practical experience that will provide transferable skills for any career they choose. We believe diversity is a strength, and we welcome all to join us! Our wide array of Media Partners means that every student can find their best fit. <br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Our Mission:<\\/strong><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Student Media empowers students<\\/em><\\/strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.<strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Our students create valued sources<\\/em><\\/strong> of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.<strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>We encourage excellence, leadership and accountability<\\/em><\\/strong> as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society. <br><\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"166\"],\"13\":[\"88\"],\"47\":\"<p>You can help further our mission! Learn about the different ways you can support us. <br><\\/p>\",\"21\":\"Through the combined effort of students and faculty, our mission is to provide a professional learning foundation for all.\"}}', '2017-05-11 03:48:43', '2017-05-11 03:48:43', '0474fa68-430c-4435-ad8b-526c4243af99'),
