 ('17', '110', 'en_us', 'Rental Listings', '[{\"col3\":\"Rental Listings\",\"col1\":\"$75\\/month\",\"col2\":\"\"}]', 'Fill your vacancies faster with a Kentcribs listing. The listing showcases your property with unlimited photos and narrative. Prospective tenants can also email or call you directly from a mobile device. Listings include: • Name • Phone • Address • Email • Web link • Photos • Price/month/unit • Apartment type • # rooms & baths • Amenities • Floor plans • Map • Unlimited narrative • Distance from KSU Student Center', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-14 21:49:58', '2017-04-14 21:50:44', 'a1d926f1-a60e-4321-95cf-6d717825197e'),
